  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Avoid school dropout in children with DownSyndrome</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The National Emergency caused by Covid 19 have prompted schools to provide care for all students virtually.This strategy has managed to mitigate the impact in terms of access to education. However, this provision fails to respond to the necessary adjustments for the population with intellectual disabilities.This project seeks virtual pedagogical support in a way that facilitates developing the academic skills required in the different grades to  avoid school dropouts</narrative>
  </description>
